name: abrarnaseer
overview: We adhere to Generally Accepted Accounting Principles as well as the standard set up by the Certified General Accountants of Ontario. As professionals, we realize how sensitive your financial data is and promise strict confidentiality. We also promise to provide you with service that is fast, friendly and reliable. We believe in building our practice on a strong foundation of client relationship. We take to get to know you, to understand your need, objective and concerns. In order to create the tailored solution that suits you best.
